{{vgname|三十航班之恋|en=Thirty Flights of Loving}}是布兰登·钟旗下[[独立游戏|独立游戏]]公司{{lang|en|[[Blendo_Games|Blendo Games]]}}开发的[[第一人称视角游戏|第一人称视角]][[冒险游戏|冒险游戏]]，2012年8月发行[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]版，同年11月发行[[MacOS|OS X]]版。布兰登·钟将{{lang|en|[[Id_Software|id Software]]}}在《[[雷神之锤II|雷神之锤II]]》首创的[[Id_Tech_2引擎|Id Tech 2引擎]]略加修改后用于游戏开发，音乐由{{lang|en|[[Idle_Thumbs|Idle Thumbs]]}}成员克里斯·雷莫作曲，主要情节是三人企图抢劫及案发后的影响。

《三十航班之恋》是2008年游戏《[[严肃的骨头|严肃的骨头]]》的续作，玩家操纵人物都是身份不明的间谍，但游戏内容没有直接联系。{{lang|en|Idle Thumbs}}为重振播客在{{lang|en|[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]}}发起众筹，《三十航班之恋》是活动奖品，发行时还附有免费的《严肃的骨头》副本。新作获电子游戏媒体普遍好评，{{lang|en|[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]}}的平均评分达88，续作《[[四边形牛仔|四边形牛仔]]》于2016年7月25日面世。

== 游戏玩法 ==
《三十航班之恋》是[[第一人称视角游戏|第一人称视角]][[冒险游戏|冒险游戏]]，估计平均通关时间为15分钟<ref name="pcgamer 13min">{{cite web | last = Smith | first = Graham | title = Thirty Flights of Loving tells a better story in 13 minutes than most games do in 13 hours | accessdate = 2020-10-04 | date = 2012-03-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200716134853/https://www.pcgamer.com/thirty-flights-of-loving-does-more-with-story-in-13-minutes-than-most-games-do-in-13-hours/ | archivedate = 2020-07-16 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.pcgamer.com/thirty-flights-of-loving-does-more-with-story-in-13-minutes-than-most-games-do-in-13-hours/ | work = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] }}</ref>。玩家使用[[方向鍵|方向鍵]]（包括{{lang|en|WASD}}键）和鼠标控制未透露姓名的间谍<ref name="DevMan">{{Cite book | last = Chung | first = Brendon | title = Thirty Flights of Loving (manual) | publisher = [[Blendo_Games|Blendo Games]] | year = 2012}}</ref>，在游戏中走私酒类。玩家与两名[[非玩家角色|非玩家角色]]合作，分别是爆破专家安妮塔（{{lang|en|Anita}}）和负责造假的博尔赫斯（{{lang|en|Borges}}）。<ref name="eurogamer review">{{cite web | url = https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-08-23-thirty-flights-of-loving-review | title = Thirty Flights of Loving Review | work = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | date = 2012-08-23 | accessdate = 2020-10-04 | first = Oli | last = Welsh | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191214214729/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-08-23-thirty-flights-of-loving-review | archivedate = 2019-12-14 | deadurl = no }}</ref>游戏过程是三人准备抢劫及事发后的影响，中间的抢劫过程省略，但从情节发展来看肯定出了岔子<ref name="eurogamer review" />。

[[File:Thirty_flights_of_loving_screenshot.jpg|thumb]]》相同的方块画风，上图中的玩家角色和博尔赫斯正在藏身处准备抢劫]]

《三十航班之恋》与《严肃的骨头》叙事结构不同，不采用直线叙事，强迫玩家通过线索和细节推断情节<ref name="eurogamer review" />。玩家执行任务期间需要同各种对象及环境互动，换取目标和指引。玩家基本不能变更游戏机制，只能自由移动，根据进度需要拾取物体。游戏中的多个阶段可以执行包括喝酒在内的几种可选操作。<ref name="eurogamer review" />

=== 情节 ===
游戏开始时，玩家从小巷经过，在此期间可以了解部分游戏元素，如移动方法和按键分配。经过酒吧和多条小巷后，安妮塔和博尔赫斯出现。接下来三人下飞机，镜头一闪，玩家看到安妮塔和博尔赫斯中枪并躺在装满板条箱的房间，玩家抬起博尔赫斯走出房间，外面看起来是机场。接下来玩家又进入光线很暗的房间，安妮塔坐在椅子上剥皮吃橘子。走过又一条小巷后，三人一起参加婚礼。

安妮塔和玩家喝醉酒，其他角色开始跳舞，在屋内飞来飞去。接下来玩家又来到暗室，看到安妮塔剥皮吃橘子，然后又出现在前面她和博尔赫斯倒地的机场房间。画面显示玩家把博尔赫斯抬上行李车离开机场，接着出现在枪战现场，再是一段骑摩托车的画面并以撞车告终，玩家随后进入博物馆。馆内有许多印有游戏名称和制作人员姓名的牌匾，玩家离开后进入新地点，这里在解释[[伯努利定律|伯努利定律]]中的低气压和高气压理论。此后玩家再度进入摩托车骑行画面，游戏至此结束。

== 开发 ==
[[File:Brendon_Chung_at_GDC_2012.jpg|thumbnail]]

《三十航班之恋》由{{lang|en|[[Blendo_Games|Blendo Games]]}}发行，布兰登·钟（{{lang|en|Brendon Chung}}）独力开发，他是{{lang|en|[[Pandemic_Studios|Pandemic Studios]]}}的[[关卡设计师|关卡设计师]]，曾参与《[[全能战士|全能战士]]》（{{lang|en|''Full Spectrum Warrior''}}）和《[[指环王：征服|指环王：征服]]》（{{lang|en|''Lord of the Rings: Conquest''}}）等游戏研发。设计师将[[Id_Software|id Software]]在《[[雷神之锤II|雷神之锤II]]》首创的[[Id_Tech_2引擎|Id Tech 2]][[游戏引擎|图形引擎]]修改后用于开发《三十航班之恋》。<ref name="Dev1">{{cite web | last = Chick | first = Tom | title = The man behind the strange wonderful world of Gravity Bone | url = http://fidgit.com/archives/2009/01/the-man-behind-the-strange-won.php | work = FidGit | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100303235810/http://fidgit.com/archives/2009/01/the-man-behind-the-strange-won.php | archivedate = 2010-03-03 | date = 2009-01-01 | publisher = Sci Fi | accessdate = 2010-03-03 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>戴维·海德（{{lang|en|David Hyde}}）和“疯狗”（{{lang|en|Mad Dog}}）共同开发“拉撒路”（{{lang|en|Lazarus}}）游戏增强插件<ref name="gamasutra igf">{{cite web | accessdate = 2020-10-04 | website = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200803232746/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/184739/Road_to_the_IGF_Blendo_Games_Thirty_Flights_of_Loving.php | archivedate = 2020-08-03 | deadurl = no | first = Mike | last = Rose | url = https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/184739/Road_to_the_IGF_Blendo_Games_Thirty_Flights_of_Loving.php | title = Road to the IGF: Blendo Games' Thirty Flights of Loving | date = 2013-01-16 }}</ref>。据布兰登·钟透露，虽已接触更新、更“强大而灵活”的游戏引擎，但他还是选择已在[[开源软件|开源平台]]发布的老引擎，这样游戏就能免费重新发布<ref name="Dev1" />。《三十航班之恋》的源代码已按第二版[[GNU通用公共许可证|GNU通用公共许可证]]发布，属[[自由软件|免费软件]]<ref>{{cite web | url = https://blendogames.com/thirtyflightsofloving/faq.htm | title = Thirty Flight of Loving FAQ | accessdate = 2020-10-04 | year = 2012 | publisher = Blendo Games | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200625170339/http://blendogames.com/thirtyflightsofloving/faq.htm | archivedate = 2020-06-25 }}</ref>。

游戏构想源自《严肃的骨头》原型，但因对话太多放弃。{{lang|en|Idle Thumbs}}后来邀请钟为[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]活动开发游戏，钟于是重启原有设想。<ref name="DevComm">Chung, Brendon. ''Thirty Flights of Loving'' (developer commentary). [[Blendo_Games|Blendo Games]] (2012)</ref>游戏主开发阶段共花费不到三个月时间，用于创建游戏内容，此后用于完善、修改[[程序错误|程序错误]]的时间更长。钟在新游戏沿用多种《严肃的骨头》已有元素<ref name="gamasutra igf" />，并采用各种工具创作游戏元素。例如{{lang|en|[[Blender|Blender]]}}创建模型，{{lang|en|[[Audacity|Audacity]]}}和{{lang|en|[[Adobe_Photoshop|Adobe Photoshop]]}}制作音效和图像纹理，游戏关卡用{{lang|en|GtkRadiant}}创作。<ref name="gamasutra igf" />

钟通过游戏环境表明玩家和非玩家角色组建的是犯罪团伙，他有意避免使用画外音，通过环境把玩家认知与主角认知之间脱节的部分联系起来<ref name="DevComm" />。安妮塔和博尔赫斯出场时本有对话介绍，但后来被删。{{lang|en|Idle Thumbs}}的工作人员觉得各人物间的关系不够明朗，所以钟又新增部分情节<ref name="DevComm" />。钟在游戏中纳入自动生成非玩家角色的系统，这样就无需手动编写游戏中每个人物的脚本。钟还进一步指出，虽然各角色可以在路途上随机游荡，但游戏偶尔会出现故障，特别是在楼梯附近。自动生成非玩家角色的代码本是为监控游戏原型设计，该游戏始终没有落实。<ref name="DevComm" />

游戏中本来有几位主要角色在街头吃面的内容，为此还专门设计第一人称视角的饮食模拟器，但在最终发布版本换成骑摩托车的桥段<ref name="DevComm" />。枪战本来配有“音乐韵律”，灵感源自纪录片《[[失衡生活|失衡生活]]》，之后同样被删<ref name="DevComm" />。最后一关的博物馆是仿照[[国家自然历史博物馆_(法国)|法国国家自然历史博物馆]]建模<ref name="DevComm" />。据钟透露，他在开发关卡前先要花时间研究，“了解事件原理”。在他看来，研究过程与游戏的特征和基础息息相关。<ref name="DevComm" />《三十航班之恋》是钟根据《雷神之锤II》系列地图“{{lang|en|Citizen Abel}}”（意为“公民阿贝乐”）设计的第七款游戏，最早的两款都是在1999年完成编程，第三到五种是在2000至2004年间编写<ref name="DevComm" />，第六种便是2008年的《严肃的骨头》，也是首款发行游戏<ref name="DevComm" />。钟通过{{lang|en|Idle Thumbs}}播客介绍包括《三十航班之恋》在内每种游戏的开发过程，这些游戏的情节都发生在同一个世界<ref name="tone control">{{cite web | url = https://www.idlethumbs.net/tonecontrol/episodes/brendon-chung | title = Tone Control - Episode 7, Brendon Chung | work = Idle Thumbs | date = 2014-01-15 | accessdate = 2020-10-04 | archivedate = 2019-07-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190721165451/https://www.idlethumbs.net/tonecontrol/episodes/brendon-chung }}</ref>。

《三十航班之恋》与《严肃的骨头》一样包含文化隐喻和[[彩蛋_(媒体)|彩蛋]]。据{{lang|en|Kickstarter}}活动透露，游戏致敬的作品和人物包括电影《[[秃鹰七十二小时|秃鹰七十二小时]]》（''{{lang|en|Three Days of the Condor}}''）、《[[窃听大阴谋|窃听大阴谋]]》（''{{lang|en|The Conversation}}''）；导演[[史蒂文·索德伯格|史蒂文·索德伯格]]、[[昆汀·塔伦蒂诺|昆汀·塔伦蒂诺]]；游戏《[[魔域|魔域]]》、《[[黑街聖徒3|黑街聖徒3]]》；动画片《[[狂歡三寶|狂歡三寶]]》、《[[航空小英雄|航空小英雄]]》等。<ref name="rps ref">{{Cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200207051823/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2013/02/01/the-27-homages-of-thirty-flights-of-loving/ | url = https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2013/02/01/the-27-homages-of-thirty-flights-of-loving/ | title = The 27 Homages Of Thirty Flights Of Loving | first = David | last = Valjalo | date = 2013-02-01 | accessdate = 2020-10-04 | work = [[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]] | archivedate = 2020-02-07 | deadurl = no }}</ref>《三十航班之恋》不再像钟过去的绝大多数游泳那样采用已有音乐作品<ref name="DevComm" />，游戏中的音乐由{{lang|en|Idle Thumbs}}成员[[克里斯·雷莫|克里斯·雷莫]]（{{lang|en|Chris Remo}}）作曲<ref name="1up 2012">{{cite web | url = http://www.1up.com/news/1up-favorite-games-2012-flights | title = 1UP's Favorite Games of 2012: Thirty Flights of Loving | first = Marty | last = Sliva | date = 2012-12-25 | accessdate = 2016-08-02 | website = [[1UP.com|1UP.com]] | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160802110953/http://www.1up.com/news/1up-favorite-games-2012-flights | archivedate = 2016-08-02 }}</ref>，其他音效由[[贾里德·爱默生-约翰逊|贾里德·爱默生-约翰逊]]（{{lang|en|Jared Emerson-Johnson}}）和[[小安东尼·洛卡西欧|小安东尼·洛卡西欧]]（{{lang|en|A.J. Locascio}}）提供，充分利用{{lang|en|Soundsnap}}网站提供的音效素材库<ref name="DevMan" />。

== 发行 ==
2012年2月，《三十航班之恋》与{{lang|en|Idle Thumbs}}为重振播客在{{lang|en|Kickstarter}}所发活动的其他项目一起公布<ref name="sequel1">{{cite web | last = Meer | first = Alec | date = 2012-02-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200803095102/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2012/02/28/gravity-bones-sequel-thirty-flights-of-loving/ | url = https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2012/02/28/gravity-bones-sequel-thirty-flights-of-loving/ | title = Gravity Bone's Sequel: Thirty Flights Of Loving | work = [[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]] | accessdate = 2020-10-05 | archivedate = 2020-08-03 }}</ref><ref name="sequel2">{{cite web | last = Hamilton | first = Kirk | date = 2012-02-28 | url = https://kotaku.com/indie-darling-gravity-bone-gets-a-sequel-5889082 | title = Indie Darling Gravity Bone Gets a Sequel | work = [[Kotaku|Kotaku]] | accessdate = 2020-10-05 | archivedate = 2020-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20201002175454/https://kotaku.com/indie-darling-gravity-bone-gets-a-sequel-5889082 }}</ref>。{{lang|en|Idle Thumbs}}团队曾与钟探讨《严肃的骨头》续作，作为{{lang|en|Kickstarter}}活动的奖品<ref name="Kicks">{{Cite web | title = Thirty Flights of Loving Trailer | date = 2012-02-28 | accessdate = 2020-10-05 | url = https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/idlethumbs/idle-thumbs-video-game-podcast/posts/181780 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190913001841/https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/idlethumbs/idle-thumbs-video-game-podcast/posts/181780 | publisher = [[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]] | archivedate = 2019-09-13 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。游戏定于2012年8月正式发行，但支持{{lang|en|Kickstarter}}众筹活动便可提前获得<ref name="steam release">{{Cite web | url = https://www.polygon.com/gaming/2012/8/21/3257862/thirty-flights-of-loving-now-available-gravity-bone | title = 'Thirty Flights of Loving' now available, includes 'Gravity Bone' | website = [[Polygon|Polygon]] | date = 2012-08-21 | accessdate = 2020-10-05 | first = Samit | last = Sarkar | archivedate = 2020-09-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200923110908/https://www.polygon.com/gaming/2012/8/21/3257862/thirty-flights-of-loving-now-available-gravity-bone }}</ref>。参与众筹还能获得正式发行版中没有的“高布伦模式”，玩家在该模式操作的人物外貌酷似男演员[[傑夫·高布倫|傑夫·高布倫]]<ref name="steam release" /><ref name="gametrailers goldblum">{{cite web | website = [[GameTrailers|GameTrailers]] | date = 2012-08-11 | accessdate = 2014-01-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140111035914/http://www.gametrailers.com/side-mission/25309/reset-thirty-flights-of-loving-is-the-best-cutscene-ever | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014-01-11 | first = Ryan | last = Stevens | url = http://www.gametrailers.com/side-mission/25309/reset-thirty-flights-of-loving-is-the-best-cutscene-ever | title = Reset: Thirty Flights of Loving is the Best Cutscene Ever }}</ref>。2012年7月，众筹活动用户可以提前在{{lang|en|[[Steam|Steam]]}}购买附有免费版《严肃的骨头》的《三十航班之恋》，其他用户需再等一个月<ref name="steam release" />。{{lang|en|[[MacOS|Mac OS X]]}}版于同年11月发布<ref name="Joystiq">{{cite web | url = http://www.joystiq.com/2012/11/14/thirty-flights-of-loving-now-seducing-mac/ | title = Thirty Flights of Loving now seducing Mac | first = David | last = Hinkle | date = 2012-11-14 | accessdate = 2015-01-31 | website = [[Joystiq|Joystiq]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150131143450/http://www.joystiq.com/2012/11/14/thirty-flights-of-loving-now-seducing-mac/ | archive-date = 2015-01-31 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

