《三十航班之恋》受到普遍好评。根据{{lang|en|[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]}}网站收集的十份评论文章，主流评论员对游戏平均评分88（最高100）<ref name="Metac" />。帕特里克·汉考克（{{lang|en|Patrick Hancock}}）在{{lang|en|[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]}}网站授予游戏9.5分好评（最高十分），声称“你眼中的直线叙事从此将大不相同”<ref name="destruct" />。

{{lang|en|[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]}}网站刊登卡罗琳·佩蒂（{{lang|en|Carolyn Petit}}）的评论，称“《三十航班之恋》的乐趣来自那些没有显示出来的事物”，包括抢劫在内的许多情节都是如此，全靠玩家推断和想象<ref name="GP1">{{Cite web | date = 2014-03-13 | accessdate = 2020-10-05 | first = Carolyn | last = Petit | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180613234631/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/thirty-flights-of-loving-one-of-the-least-reviewable-games-of-the-year/1100-6397958/ | archivedate = 2018-06-13 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.gamespot.com/articles/thirty-flights-of-loving-one-of-the-least-reviewable-games-of-the-year/1100-6397958/ | title = Thirty Flights of Loving: One of the Least Reviewable Games of the Year | work = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] }}</ref>。《{{lang|en|[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]}}》杂志的格雷厄姆·史密斯（{{lang|en|Graham Smith}}）对游戏的极简叙事风格推崇备至，断言《三十航班之恋》用13分钟讲的故事比绝大多数游戏花13个小时表达得更好<ref name="pcgamer 13min" />。马克·布朗（{{lang|en|Mark Brown}}）在《[[联线英国|联线英国]]》（''{{lang|en|Wired UK}}''）杂志发文，称赞钟充满信心和派头地交出又一部令人难忘的作品……“采用15年前的游戏引擎制作，前后20分钟内没有任何配音，画面充满金属光泽，以超短篇幅讲述立方体抢劫的故事”<ref name="wired1">{{cite web | last = Brown | first = Mark | title = Dramatic, minimalist 30 Flights of Loving is a heist game without the heist | url = https://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2012-08/22/30-flights-of-loving | work = Wired UK | accessdate = 2016-04-02 | date = 2012-08-22 | archivedate = 2016-04-02 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160402202749/https://www.wired.co.uk/news/archive/2012-08/22/30-flights-of-loving }}</ref>。

{{lang|en|[[IGN|IGN]]}}网站刊登内森·穆尼尔（{{lang|en|Nathan Meunier}}）的评论，赞扬游戏从一开始就令人着迷，只要短短几分钟就令玩家把之前的所有设想和期待抛诸脑后，全心全意投入其中<ref name="ign review" />。英国电子游戏杂志《[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]]》感觉《三十航班之恋》仿佛耐人寻味的心理惊悚片，就像[[魏斯·安德森|魏斯·安德森]]重拍[[亞弗列·希治閣|希区柯克]]的作品<ref name="edge review" />。文中认可游戏“奇妙且模凌两可”的情节，“以巧妙取景和精细制作取代对话，以随时可能切换的跳跃剪辑启动过场动画，令游戏体验更上一层楼”<ref name="edge review" />。希腊杂志《个人计算机大师》（''{{lang|en|PC Master}}''）同样称赞游戏叙事风格，声称《三十航班之恋》“企图模糊游戏与艺术的界限”<ref name="pcmaster">{{cite journal | title = Thirty Flights of Loving review | journal = PC Master | date = 2012-10 | location = Greece}}</ref>。《三十航班之恋》入围2013年[[独立游戏节|独立游戏节]]叙事奖，但最终不敌理查德·霍夫迈尔（{{lang|en|Richard Hofmeier}}）的《[[小贩人生|小贩人生]]》（''{{lang|en|Cart Life}}''，2011年）<ref name=IGF-Winners>{{cite news | title = 2013 Independent Games Festival Winners & Finalists | url = http://www.igf.com/2013finalistswinners.html | work = [[独立游戏节|Independent Games Festival]] | accessdate = 2016-09-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160923035906/http://www.igf.com/2013finalistswinners.html | archivedate = 2016-09-23 | location = United States | year = 2013 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

== 续作 ==
《四边形牛仔》（''{{lang|en|Quadrilateral Cowboy}}''）是《三十航班之恋》的续作，由布兰登·钟开发，2016年7月25日发行。游戏情节与两部前作发生在同一宇宙但没有直接联系，围绕负责监督特工侵入建筑盗取文件的黑客展开。<ref name="eurogamer preview">{{cite web | date = 2013-02-06 | accessdate = 2020-10-05 | first = Jeffrey | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20181212200204/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-02-06-thirty-flights-of-loving-dev-shows-off-upcoming-cyberpunk-game-quadrilateral-cowboy | archivedate = 2018-12-12 | last = Matulef | url = https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-02-06-thirty-flights-of-loving-dev-shows-off-upcoming-cyberpunk-game-quadrilateral-cowboy | title = Thirty Flights of Loving dev shows off upcoming cyberpunk game Quadrilateral Cowboy | work = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | deadurl = no }}</ref>新作不再沿用前作的{{lang|en|Id Tech}} 2引擎，而是采用《[[毁灭战士3|毁灭战士3]]》中的[[Id_Tech_4引擎|id Tech 4引擎]]。据钟透露，与老版相比，新引擎提供“更多更加现代的功能”。<ref name="ign preview">{{cite web | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2013/02/04/what-the-hell-is-quadrilateral-cowboy | title = What the Hell is Quadrilateral Cowboy? | first = Colin | last = Campbell | date = 2013-02-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190825070410/https://www.ign.com/articles/2013/02/04/what-the-hell-is-quadrilateral-cowboy | archivedate = 2019-08-25 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-10-05 | work = [[IGN|IGN]] }}</ref>

